  "decision_conditions": [
    "The proposed roof lights, by virtue of their siting and number,  would detract from the special character and appearance of the of the dwelling, which is a Grade II Listed Building.  As such,  the proposed works  are contrary to Policies CD9 and CD2 of the Adopted Unitary Development Plan (1998) and  Policies 41 of the Revised Unitary Development Plan (2004). \r\r",
    "The proposed internal works would have a detrimental impact on the special interest of the of the Grade II Listed Building and therefore are contrary to Policies CD2 and CD9 of the Adopted Unitary Development Plan (1998) and Policy 41 of the Revised Deposit Unitary Development Plan (2004).",
    "Your attention is drawn to the provisions of The Party Wall Act 1996 in relation to the rights of adjoining owners regarding party walls etc.  These rights are a matter for civil enforcement and you may wish to consult a surveyor or architect.",
    "Your attention is drawn to the need to comply with the requirements of the Control of Pollution Act 1974 concerning construction site noise and in this respect you are advised to contact the Council's Environmental Health Division."
